name: Muhammad K. Rezza
review: This stadium has just been extremely renovated and now it features sophisticated design and facilities. It's gonna be the new pride of Semarang citizen and also PSIS supporters especially.

name: Imam Santosa
review: I actually like this place a lot because it such a huge sport area where there are lots of facilities such as stadium, swimming pool etc. But this particular stadium is huge! It is now under construction and probably within 6 months the whole stadium will be finished for its construction. I like to run there because the one lap around stadium, you will get around 700m. Plus the place is quiet and there are lots of shades. Hopefully the government will add more rubbish bin to encourage people to throw rubbish properly. Whenever there is PSIS Day, this place will be so crowded! I think the local football fans are looking forward to have the renovation and construction done.

name: Bang Moen
review: (Translated by Google) In front of the stadium there is a morning market every Sunday. At 6 am already at the title of their respective stalls. Sometimes on certain mornings there is an exercise group in the parking area. For those whose SIM is about to expire, don't worry. Come here at 7 am every Monday-Saturday (because the quota is limited), prepare an fc ID card and fc driver's license, fill out forms, psychological tests, medical tests and after the officers come wait for the call to take a photo of the driver's license. Shhh... there's a "fast track" you know. For those who want to take care of extending the validity period of their vehicle registration, you can also come here every Monday-Wednesday, from 9 to 12. (Original) Di depan stadion ada pasar pagi setiap hari Minggu. Jam 6 pagi sudah pada gelar lapak masing-masing. Kadang pada pagi hari tertentu ada grup senam di area parkirnya. Buat yang SIM nya mau habis masa berlakunya, jangan kuatir. Datanglah ke sini jam 7 pagi tiap Senin-Sabtu (sebab kuota terbatas), siapkan fc KTP dan fc SIM, isi formulir, tes psikotes, tes kesehatan dan setelah petugas datang nunggu panggilan untuk foto SIM. Sstt... ada "jalur cepatnya" lho. Buat yang mau mengurus perpanjangan masa berlaku STNK kendaraannya, bisa datang juga ke sini tiap Senin-Rabu, jam 9 sampai jam 12 aja.

review: (Translated by Google) Not bad, but please fix the worship facilities and public toilets.. (Original) Lumayan lah tapi mohon diperbaiki fasilitas ibadah dan toilet umum nya..

name: Wintaka Ari Bawa
review: (Translated by Google) The stadium has been recently renovated and uses synthetic grass on the surface of the field. Single seat seats in the western stands are still too tight in my opinion. It is quite difficult if you want to walk past a bench that has been occupied by other spectators because the space is only really for legroom when sitting alone. Then the supporting pillars also block the view towards the field. Many people want a stadium without a running track, but I am not comfortable watching a match in a stadium without a running track because players who run on the sides of the field are not clearly visible due to obstruction of the guardrail. But as much appreciation to the city government of Semarang and Central Java as they have tried to improve the facilities in this Citarum stadium. (Original) Stadion yang baru direnovasi dan menggunakan rumput sintetis pada permukaan lapangan. Kursi single seat di tribun barat masih terlalu mepet menurut saya. Cukup kesulitan apabila ingin berjalan melewati bangku yang sudah diduduki penonton lain karena space yang ada hanya benar2 untuk ruang kaki ketika duduk saja. Kemudian pilar2 penyangga juga menghalangi pandangan ke arah lapangan. Banyak yang menginginkan stadion tanpa track lari, namun saya justru kurang nyaman menyaksikan pertandingan di stadion tanpa track lari karena pemain yang berlari di sisi pinggir lapangan tidak terlihat jelas akibat terhalang pagar pembatas. Tapi apresiasi sebesar-besarnya kepada pemerintah kota Semarang dan Jawa tengah karena sudah berusaha memperbaiki fasilitas di stadion Citarum ini.

name: Rina A
review: (Translated by Google) The stadium is pretty close to Semarang city center. About 5km from the intersection, with a distance of approximately 15 minutes from the intersection. The stadium building is good and quite maintained. The gate is usually opened when there is an event. The stands are good and have a roof for the west side. The field is arguably the standard. Usually the stadium is used for league competition 3. Around the stadium, many food stalls (especially in front) are quite strategic. (Original) Stadionnya lumayan dekat dari pusat kota semarang. Sekitar 5km dari simpanglima, dengan jarak tempuh kurang lebih 15 menit dari simpanglima. Bangunan stadionnya bagus dan cukup terjaga. Gerbangnya biasanya dibuka pas ada event aja. Tribunnya bagus dan beratap sih untuk sisi barat. Lapangannya bisa dibilang standard. Biasanya stadion ini dipakai untuk kompetisi liga 3. Di sekitar stadion banyak warung warung makan (terutama di depan) cukup strategis sih lokasinya.
